275
00:15:10,000 --> 00:15:13,000
Oh, much.

276
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,000
Who are you?

277
00:15:16,000 --> 00:15:20,000
Oh, more ask who I was.

278
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:23,000
Don't tell me you had to ask a question.

279
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:25,000
Who were you?

280
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:29,000
In life, I was your partner, Jacob Marley.

281
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:32,000
Okay, so he's dead.

282
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:35,000
Yes, seven years, this night, Ebeneezer Scrooge.

283
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:38,000
I said that earlier today, I know.

284
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,000
So why are you here?

285
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,000
I must! It is commanded by me!

286
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:48,000
I must wander the world and see what I can no longer share.

287
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:52,000
And what I would not share when I walked where you do.

288
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,000
Yeah, no, that's fucking confusing.

289
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:57,000
So you, like, have to do something with the chain?

290
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:58,000
I don't know.

291
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,000
The chains, look at them.

292
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,000
