293
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:06,000
They are locks and bolts and gold coins.

294
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,000
Seems heavy.

295
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,000
I forged them.

296
00:16:09,000 --> 00:16:13,000
I crafted them with deco pot.

297
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:17,000
Each link, each day, when I sat in these chairs,

298
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:21,000
commanded these rooms, greet Ebeneezer and Vel,

299
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:24,000
feel them, know them.

300
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:29,000
Yours was as heavy as this I wear seven years ago,

301
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:33,000
and you have labored to build it since.

302
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:38,000
So, if you're here to, like, give me a talk and lecture me and stuff,

303
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:39,000
like, I don't have time for that.

304
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:42,000
It's really late, it's cold, I don't know if you know that,

305
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,000
and I would like my comforts now.

306
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:45,000
Oh, I have no comfort for you.

307
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:49,000
I know not how you see me this night.

308
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:50,000
I did not ask it.

309
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:54,000
I was like, Scrooge, I don't want to see him, not on Christmas.

310
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:57,000
I have sat invisible beside you many and many a day.

311
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:58,000
That's creepy.

312
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:01,000
Wishing that I could see you, but not tonight specifically.

313
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:06,000
I was out on a date, and then they sent me here with these chains again.

314
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:09,000
I am commanded to bring you a chance, Ebeneezer.

315
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,000
Heed it!

316
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:12,000
Okay, get on with it then.

317
00:17:12,000 --> 00:17:18,000
You are going to be haunted tonight by three spirits.

318
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,000
Is that, is that, yeah, okay.

319
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,000
Yeah, yeah, mark it, three spirits.

320
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:27,000
Yeah, no, no, I don't, no, I will not mark it.

321
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:31,000
Oh, then I will walk where I do.

322
