357
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,000
Oh, black.

358
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,000
Oh, twelve midnight.

359
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,000
Pause.

360
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:09,000
I must get up, it's a day wasted.

361
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,000
I gotta get down to the office.

362
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,000
Two small chimes are heard.

363
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:16,000
Well, that's quarter past, but it just rang twelve.

364
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:19,000
Fifteen minutes hasn't gone past, that's too fast.

365
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:21,000
Again, two small chimes are heard.

366
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,000
It's a quarter to one.

367
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:27,000
The spirit, Molly said he would come at one.

368
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:31,000
He hurries to his bed as the chimes ring again.

369
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,000
One.

370
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:50,000
The hour is struck again by a large street clock and the first spirit appears.

371
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:54,000
