I am the ghost of Christmas past.

376
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:22,000
Like, like long past, like yesterday, like five years ago.

377
00:20:22,000 --> 00:20:25,000
Your past.

378
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:29,000
So why are you here?

379
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:32,000
Your welfare.

380
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,000
Rise, walk with me.

381
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:40,000
Okay, but I'm just like a mortal person and I can't just float through the air.

382
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:42,000
My hand.

383
