The spirit motions for Scrooge to turn and he sees a young boy playing with a teddy bear and talking to it.

401
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:36,000
Yeah, reading.

402
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,000
Poor kid.

403
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,000
What?

404
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,000
I wonder.

405
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:40,000
Reading?

