And jewels I shall bring you and gold and myrrh and frankincense.

415
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,000
And they put him down.

416
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,000
Do you remember?

417
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:13,000
That silly one at the gate of Damascus in his under drawers asleep.

418
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,000
Yes.

419
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,000
Yes.

420
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:19,000
The genie turned the sultan's groom upside down and stood him on his head.

421
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,000
Served him right, I say.

422
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:23,000
And all the thieves and the jars of oil.

423
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:26,000
Scrooge pretends to stab the jars of oil with his scimitar.

424
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,000
Yes.

425
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,000
Yes.

426
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,000
And running them true.

427
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:31,000
This and this and this for each of you.

428
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,000
Yes.

429
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:33,000
And remember?

430
00:22:33,000 --> 00:22:34,000
Do you remember?

