And he used to sit on the very top of the tree up there.

439
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:59,000
And Robinson Crusoe sailed around the island.

440
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:01,000
And he thought the parrot said.

441
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:03,000
The parrot said.

442
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:06,000
Robinson Crusoe, where you been?

443
00:23:06,000 --> 00:23:08,000
Robinson Crusoe, where you been?

444
